&quot;so i start to run him back to the rest of the guild and we start in on him. during the fight, my war who was MT goes down (along with a druid i think). so our ranger kites him around while my war gets rezzed and loots his gear. after gear is looted the ranger yells something about people attacking Lodi and so we all run up to where our ranger was.&quot;<br>
